{
  "description": "A sweeping aerial view showcases a dense urban landscape meeting the expanse of a bay. The city is a patchwork of buildings, primarily low to mid-rise, stretching across a wide area. A prominent church spire and several larger institutional buildings punctuate the urban fabric. The bay is calm, reflecting the warm hues of the setting sun. A bridge spans the bay, connecting to distant hills. The sky is dramatically lit with fiery oranges and yellows near the horizon, transitioning to cooler tones of blue and grey higher up. Wispy clouds are scattered across the sky, adding texture and depth. The overall impression is one of vastness and tranquility.",
